text: Neetu Singh is a Indian actress that is well known for appearing in Hindi films made through the years 1960 to 1980. In the year 2012, she was put on the Walk of the Stars in Mumbai. She started her acting career in the movie Suraj, released in the year 1960. == References == Category:1958 births Category:Indian actors Category:Actors in Hindi cinema Category:People from Delhi
title: Neetu Singh
